{
  "texts": [
    "Through my experience, I've learned the importance of clear communication and am continually working on strategies to overcome linguistic barriers and deliver effective feedback that promotes learning and understanding.",
    "Eleven out of nineteen participants (57.9%) acknowledged facing linguistic barriers when delivering feedback to students.",
    "These educators found it challenging to choose the most appropriate words or expressions to convey their messages clearly.",
    "Hayden stated: 'I know what I want to say but finding the right words to say it can be difficult at times'.",
    "Those participants who were aware of linguistic barriers in delivering feedback suggested ways to overcome such challenges."
  ]
}